{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-065__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-001", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-065", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-065__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "老子 65.1", "sort_key": "065.001", "text_original": "古之善為道者，非以明民，將以愚之。", "text_normalized": "古之善為道者，非以明民，將以愚之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-065__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-002", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-065", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-065__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "老子 65.2", "sort_key": "065.002", "text_original": "民之難治，以其智多。", "text_normalized": "民之難治，以其智多。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-065__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-003", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-065", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-065__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "老子 65.3", "sort_key": "065.003", "text_original": "故以智治國，國之賊，", "text_normalized": "故以智治國，國之賊，", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-065__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-004", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-065", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-065__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "老子 65.4", "sort_key": "065.004", "text_original": "不以智治國，國之福。知此兩者亦稽式。常知稽式，是謂玄德。玄德深矣，遠矣，", "text_normalized": "不以智治國，國之福。知此兩者亦稽式。常知稽式，是謂玄德。玄德深矣，遠矣，", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-065__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-005", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-065", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-065__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "老子 65.5", "sort_key": "065.005", "text_original": "與物反矣，", "text_normalized": "與物反矣，", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-065__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-006", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-065", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-065__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "老子 65.6", "sort_key": "065.006", "text_original": "然後乃至大順。", "text_normalized": "然後乃至大順。", "notes": ""}
